==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lote
<hw>Lote</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>lotus</ets>, Gr.
<?/. Cf. <er>Lotus</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A large tree
(<spn>Celtis australis</spn>), found in the south of Europe. It has a
hard wood, and bears a cherrylike fruit. Called also <altname>nettle
tree</altname>.</def> <rj><au>Eng. Cyc.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

