HEADWORD: Lote
<hw>Lote</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>lotte</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The European burbot.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lote</ent>⟦br⟧

